\pard\fi720\sl-243\slmult0\tx9291\i0 At the end of the path was a rock overhang, under\f1\-\f0 neath which Vivien, Sister Nuba, and the children had cre\f1\-\f0 ated a temporary home. \ldblquote It\rquote s adequate for now,\rdblquote  Vivien said, chatting idly and offering Johann a hot herbal drink from the pot hanging above the fire, \ldblquote at least until Kwame and the others arrive. Then we\rquote ll build some real houses. Kwame says that the wood here is much better for con\f1\-\f0 struction than it was where we were living before.\rdblquote\par
