\pard\fi720\sl-238\slmult0\tx9291 where we used to live,\rdblquote  Vivien said, answering Johann\rquote s un\f1\-\f0 spoken question. \ldblquote It\rquote s not tobacco, and there\rquote s not much of a buzz, but hey, it makes me feel good to watch the smoke coming out of my mouth.\rdblquote\par
