and having sex with Satoko, but could not confirm any\-thing because Satoko wouldn\rquote t implicate him, I told Kwame that we should catch Yasin in the act and then dismember him. Well, we did catch him all right, but we gave him his freedom by error?\par
Johann continued his story, describing Yasin\rquote s first at\f1\-\f0 tack on Beatrice, Johann\rquote s own imprisonment, Yasin\rquote s out\f1\-\f0 rageous suggestion that they should share Beatrice, and her eventual sexual humiliation and total denigration.\par
\ldblquote Why does God let people like that exist?\rdblquote  Vivien ex\f1\-\f0 ploded at one point. When Johann told of his escape from prison and Yasin\rquote s death, Vivien applauded. \ldblquote Good for you, giant Johann,\rdblquote  she said. \ldblquote You finally gave that bastard what he deserved\rdblquote\par
