\ldblquote Yes, yes, Nuba,\rdblquote  Vivien said. \ldblquote Thank you for reminding me... My feelings about Yasin are still so negative that it\rquote s difficult for me to understand that he too is one of God\rquote s creatures. There are aspects of Christian charity that are sometimes beyond my comprehension?\par
