\pard\fi720\sl-243\slmult0\qj\tx9291 that had happened to any of them thus far was irrefutable proof of either point of view Vivien\rquote s comments suggested that she could accept either explanation of the true nature of their hosts. Sometimes she agreed with Johann, some-tunes with Sister Nuba.\par
\ldblquote Besides,\rdblquote  Vivien said near the end of their discussion, as a mother these infinite issues do not occupy much of my energy. I am more interested in \i how \i0 we are going to live, on a day-to-day basis, than in what power is control\f1\-\f0 ling our microcosm.\rdblquote\par
