\pard\fi720\sl-238\slmult0\qj\tx9291\ldblquote What I want the council to consider, based on this latest information, is whether our decision to move might have been a bit hasty Given what I saw this evening, and Fernando\rquote s report on the number of squibbits living on the other side of the chasm, it seems unlikely that we will be able to farm over there. Besides, although the squibbits may be a manageable nuisance, do we know for certain that there are not other larger, more dangerous creatures living m our chosen area? Maybe we should do some more careful exploration before making any final decisions.\rdblquote\par
