\f3\ldblquote I have never stopped loving you,\rdblquote  he said falteringly \ldblquote with every fiber of my being. Even now, \f2 as I look at you, I know the joy of that love and I am thrilled by its power. To have been alive, and to have experienced that kind of love, makes all the pain of life \f3 meaningless and insignificant.\rdblquote\f2\par
