\f3\ldblquote She has never, \i\f2 eve\f3 n\f2  \i0\f3 been forced to be accountable for her actions,\rdblquote  Beatrice had said to Johann with rancor. \ldblquote She has not had to live by the same rules as the rest of us.\f2\par
\f3 Even now, you are still making excuses for her. It\rquote s not our fault that their crops are poor. And it certainly does not jus\f2\-\f3 tify their thievery.\rdblquote\f2\par
