\f3 As always, she was smiling. \ldblquote So we meet again, Brother Johann,\rdblquote  she said, \ldblquote one final time, on a new and different world.\rdblquote\par
 \ldblquote One final time?\rdblquote  Johann asked haltingly, still awe-struck by her presence.\f2\par
