\f3 Beatrice nodded. \ldblquote But that\rquote s the only question I am al\f2\-\f3 lowed to answer,\rdblquote  she said. \ldblquote Everything else, Brother Jo\f2\-\f3 hann, you must figure out for yourself.\rdblquote\f2\par
\f3 The glowing bright light, which had been stationed a few kilometers away during their entire conversation, now started moving toward them. \ldblquote We have only a minute or so left, Brother Johann,\rdblquote  the white Beatrice said hurriedly, \ldblquote and I didn\rquote t want to forget to tell you what a big help Sister Nuba has been to me.\f2\par
