\f3\ldblquote I know,\rdblquote  he heard her voice say. Her figure had now been engulfed by the light. \ldblquote And you have been a won\f2\-\f3 derful father for Maria, Brother Johann. Especially today. Thanks for everything.\rdblquote\f2\par
