EVEN THOUGH IT was very late, everyone in the West Village was still awake when Johann arrived. During his walk down the side of Black Rock, Johann had decided not to say anything just yet about the apparition of Beatrice. He did, however, explain the arrangement he had negoti\-ated with Maria and the others, and that Jomo, Keiko, and Satoko would be temporarily moving back to the West Vil\-lage in a few days.\par
