Maria glanced back and forth from the ribbon to Jo\-\f3 hann. \ldblquote It \i\f2 talked \i0\f3 to you,\rdblquote  she said incredulously. \ldblquote And you \i\f2 understood \i0\f3 it?\rdblquote\f2\par
\f3 Johann laughed again. \ldblquote Yes:\rquote  he said. \ldblquote But that should not surprise you. I am not an \i\f2 exact \i0 resurrection of the Jo\-hann who was your grandfather or great-grandfather. I have been given some additional \f3 capability.\rdblquote\f2\par
\f3 Maria looked at the ribbon again. \ldblquote But I\rquote m not ready to go yet,\rdblquote  she protested. \ldblquote I have so \f2 many \f3 more questions.\rdblquote\f2\par
\f3\ldblquote You really have no choice:\rquote  Johann said.\f2\par
