\f3\ldblquote I haven\rquote t been completely honest with you,\rdblquote  he said. \ldblquote I loved Beatrice with a passion beyond any feeling I ever experienced in my life. She was beyond my \f2 wildest expec\-tations as a friend, a companion, and a lover. I never really recovered from \f3 her death.\rdblquote\f2\par
